SUMMARY:VIP Reception: Staying Alive
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special evening celebrating the opening of our newest special exhibition – Staying Alive! \nBe among the first to experience our exciting new exhibition bringing the untamed animal kingdom to life. Featuring live animals\, larger-than-life sculptures\, and interactive experiences\, this exhibition showcases fascinating animal adaptations from around the world. \nSip\, snack\, and mingle with the live animal ambassadors before the exhibition opens to the public. \nTickets: Two complimentary tickets can be reserved by Curator\, Naturalist\, Explorers and Brimley Society Members (tickets will be made complimentary by an automatic discount applied at checkout). Admission is $25/person for Individual Plus and Family Members. \nCurrent membership and pre-registration required. You must be 21 years or older to attend this event. ID required for entry. \nNot a Member yet? Join today! \nSpace is limited\, reserve your tickets today!
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/staying-alive-vip-reception/
LOCATION:Downtown Raleigh\, 11 West Jones Street\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27601\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adults,Member Exclusive,Special Events
